	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Sedit quidam simulans se non esse malum evangelicum in <placeName ref="l2736">Wallenburg</placeName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><placeName ref="l2736">Waldenburg</placeName> (<placeName ref="l612">Kt. Basel-Land</placeName>).</note>, oppidulo ditionis nostrę, qui usus est in publico hospitio his verbis:</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="de">Wenn der keiser nit in 4 wuchen zuͦ <placeName ref="l587">Zurich</placeName> in der stadt ist oder sy doch schwerlich belegert, so höw man mir den kopf ab, und die <foreign xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l2448">Quinquepagici</placeName> prodent ipsos</foreign>."</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p20445">Parochus Wallenburgensis</persName><note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="p20445">Wilhelm Hildtoch</persName>; s. Karl Gauß, Basilea reformata, Basel 1930, S. 34.</note> hęc mihi.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Indignabar, quod hospes non protinus indicabat hunc pręfecto, ut amplius fuisset interrogatus; sed evaserat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Talia et in pago <placeName ref="l2028">Riechen</placeName>, etiam ditionis nostrę, fuit, qui de Confoederatis invadendis a Cęsare certo adfirmavit.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Esto vero nugę sint; scire tamen tam dura non nocet, ut, contra quos ea parantur, sint paratiores; nam, si vera sunt, prodest novisse, modo nos cautiores effecerint, sin aliter, scivisse non obest.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la">De animo Cęsaris dubium non est; durius existit, quod dictum est de reliquis.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la">Equidem melius sperare de his me posse vellem.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale cum tuis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" ana="salute"><persName ref="p8011">Gvaltherum</persName> salutabis et <persName ref="p8459">Ottonem</persName>.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la"><placeName ref="l28">Basileę</placeName> 2. augusti anno 1550.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la">Tuus <persName ref="p8418">Os[valdus] Myconius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la">Hęc in aures tibi, nisi sit, ubi tuto queas uti, praesertim de <placeName ref="l2448">Quinque</placeName> etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la">D. <persName ref="p495">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, in domino suo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
